_sText:
“gg_one_tower”

This is a small map with very fast game play that takes place in a castle setting.  The map has three levels of play: ground level, walkway level and tower level.  Buy Zones are included for people who want to play the map fight yard style.

-	36 spawn points, 18 per team
-	Overview radar
-	Cubemaps
-	Optimized with nodraw for better FPS
-	Nav file for bots
-	Buy Zones
-	Custom textures by CGTextures at www.cgtextures.com
-	Custom skybox by Jaj
-	All files packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
